snippet.title: Baby Storm || Nintendo Switch Trailer
snippet.description:
Baby Storm - Play now on Nintendo Switch 
🧸 https://bit.ly/BabyStormNS

Buy your physical edition at
🎁 www.forever-limited.com 

Baby Storm is a cooperative party game. 
Watch over unpredictable kids as they unleash chaos in your kindergarten! Maintain order, run, clean and feed your way to the highest score, in solo or up to 4 players!
